Package org.odpi.openmetadata.samples.governanceactions.clinicaltrials

package org.odpi.openmetadata.samples.governanceactions.clinicaltrials
Coco Pharmaceuticals governance actions for clinical trials - they run in the ClinicalTrials@CocoPharmaceuticals governance engine.
